Package: motifcounter
Type: Package
Title: R package for analysing TFBSs in DNA sequences
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2016
Author: Wolfgang Kopp [aut, cre]
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat,
